results.name: Black White
results.title: Balenciaga Speed Graffiti Trainers Black White
results.description:
The Balenciaga Speed Graffiti Trainers Black White fuse athletic aesthetics with artistic flair, and in doing so, redefine the boundaries between fashion and contemporary art.

These shoes are renowned for their sock-like construction, which is crafted from a breathable and flexible stretch-knit material. Their standout feature, however, is the graffiti-inspired artwork adorning the sides of the soles. The soles' white backgrounds allow the brand’s name to pop in black lettering that matches the solid colorway of the upper. A textured base to the rubber outsole provides reliable traction and durability for these shoes.

What our experts love the most about the Balenciaga Speed Graffiti Trainers Black White, however, is the absence of laces and any other extraneous details that would compromise the intentionally minimalist nature of these shoes. They released for the very first time on November 1, 2019, with an original price tag of $795.

results.name: Black
results.title: Balenciaga Track Black
results.description:
The Balenciaga Track Black was launched as the next addition to the women’s sports collection in the Balenciaga brand.

The Balenciaga Track Black is made of mesh and nylon material. The sneaker comes in 100% black color at the upper part and white contrast extra laces. The size of the shoe is written at the edge of the toe, ‘Track’ branded at the back, and ‘Balenciaga’ embossed at the tongue and exterior. It features a sole that has been designed with an augmented back.

The Balenciaga Track Black was released on September 3rd, 2018 at a retail price of $975.

results.name: Black White Red (2018 Reissue)
results.title: Balenciaga Triple S Black White Red (2018 Reissue)
results.description:
The Balenciaga Triple S Black White Red (2018 Reissue) is a bold statement piece that revolutionized the sneaker scene. Launched on September 21, 2017, for $795, this sneaker reissue captures the chunky aesthetic that has become synonymous with Balenciaga's disruptive approach to fashion. The black, white, and red colorway provides a striking contrast that makes this shoe as much a work of art as it is a fashion statement.

Featuring a triple-stacked sole and a pre-distressed look, the Triple S sneaker is both an homage to sneaker cultures of the past and a forward-looking symbol of the luxury streetwear movement. Designed for the fashion-forward individual, this sneaker pushes boundaries and challenges conventional aesthetics.

Since its reissue on September 21, 2017, for $795, the Balenciaga Triple S Black White Red has been adorning the feet of style connoisseurs, standing as an icon of the luxury sneaker revolution.

results.name: Black White (2021)
results.title: Balenciaga Speed Trainer Black White (2021)
results.description: The Balenciaga Speed Trainer Black White 2021 is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines comfort and fashion. The upper is made of a stretchy knit material that conforms to your foot, while the sole is made of durable rubber for long-lasting wear. The black and white colorway is timeless and versatile, making it easy to pair with any outfit. This shoe was released on January 1st, 2021, and retails for $825. Whether you're running errands or hitting the gym, the Balenciaga Speed Trainer Black White 2021 is the perfect choice for those who want to look good and feel comfortable at the same time.
